						<summary>

						<p>Broken slab, side face near the Surabhēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Krōdhi, Phālguṇa śu. 15, Monday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Purport not clear. Seems to refer to some gift of land for the merit of Vennasāni. In characters of about the 13th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
